(221, 1, '2014-05-14 16:21:33', '2014-05-14 06:21:33', '<p class="grid_12">1.申请人资料：</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_2">你的名字<br />\r\n    [text your-name]\r\n</p> \r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_3">出生日期<br />\r\n[date dob]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_3">联系电话<br />\r\n[tel phone]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_3">你的邮箱<br />\r\n    [email your-email] </p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_12">性别<br />\r\n[select sex "男" "女"]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_12">如在澳，所持签证类别<br />\r\n[text visa]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_3" >雅思成绩(或预测成绩):平均分 <br />\r\n[text ielts]\r\n<p class="grid_2" >听[text listen]</p>\r\n<p class="grid_2" >说[text speak]</p>\r\n<p class="grid_2" >读[text reading ]</p>\r\n<p class="grid_2" >写[text writing]</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_12">雅思参加时间<br />\r\n[date ielts-date]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">2.学历情况:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_5">学历<br />\r\n[select degree "初中" "高中" "中专" "大专" "本科" "研究生" "博士生"]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_5">学制<br />\r\n[select year "2年" "3年" "4年" "5年"]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_3">最高学历毕业时间<br />\r\n[date graduate-date]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_4">毕业学校<br />\r\n[text visa]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_4">专业<br />\r\n[text visa]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">3.工作经验:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">最近工作经验所从事职业<br />\r\n[textarea work-experience x10]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_5">最近工作经验起始时间\r\n[date start]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_5">最近工作经验结束时间\r\n[date end]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">如有一段以上工作经验,请提供更多信息<br />\r\n[textarea more-experience x10]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">4.澳洲亲属情况:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">如申请人在澳洲有亲属， 请填写：<br />\r\n[textarea relatives x10]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">是否澳洲永居或公民<br />\r\n[select pr "是" "否"]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">5.澳洲学习情况:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="grid_12">是否完成两年以上学习<br />\r\n[select study-in-au "是" "否"]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_4">专业<br />\r\n[text major]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_4">完成学习的时间<br />\r\n[date graduate-year]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_12">其他需要说明的情况或要求<br />\r\n[textarea relatives x10]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_12">您希望我们用哪种方式告知评估结果\r\n[select contact-way "电子邮件" "联系电话"]\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p  class="grid_3">[submit "发送"]</p>\r\n<p  class="grid_3"><input type="reset" value="重置" /></p>\r\n\r\n<br class="clear" />\n[your-name][date dob][tel phone]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\n发件人：[your-name] <[your-email]>\r\n主题：[your-subject]\r\n\r\n留言正文：\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\n这封邮件通过联系表单【Southpac Services (http://localhost/southpac)】发送\nsouth.pac@hotmail.com\n\n\n\n\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\n留言正文：\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\n这封邮件通过联系表单【Southpac Services (http://localhost/southpac)】发送\n[your-email]\n\n\n\n你的留言已经成功发送。谢谢\n你的留言发送失败。请稍后再尝试发送或者使用其他方法联系管理员。\n出现验证错误。请检查所有内容，再重新提交。\n你的留言发送失败。请稍后再尝试发送或者使用其他方法联系管理员。\n请接受条款，然后进行下一步。\n请填写必填项。\n你输入的验证码不正确\n数字格式无效\n这个数字太小。\n这个数字太大。\n邮件地址无效。\n链接无效。\n电话号码无效\n你的回答不正确。\n日期格式不正确\n这个日期太早。\n这个日期太晚\n上传文件失败\n这种文件类型不被允许。\n这个文件太大。\n上传文件失败。发生错误。', '评估表格', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e8%af%84%e4%bc%b0%e8%a1%a8%e6%a0%bc', '', '', '2014-06-23 12:04:55', '2014-06-23 02:04:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/southpac/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=221', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
